37db6f52dceef2f","tid":740323,"uid":73092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T23:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/071845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F071845_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cbf1a7f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70724ee86d2abe7a0773add9c1a5a878d0299b41","tid":740323,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T23:19:51.000Z","msg":"Fb page 漫畫 一個人<br />\n珀麗居民好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115148_9a97f34099ad4cceda9f83709f68cf45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115148_9a97f34099ad4cceda9f83709f68cf45.png&h=c6564b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一百蚊一程？次次搭的士就唔好講野啦<br />\n搵狗鐵去比做乜野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115149_5cbb671778be4cc23c530b5973e52028.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115149_5cbb671778be4cc23c530b5973e52028.png&h=7cecd3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駁唔到就妖化他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115151_2746d3ef8e9742055503dd9c79ecf9b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115151_2746d3ef8e9742055503dd9c79ecf9b3.png&h=96048556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加價合理？係咪架。<br />\n加價減服務就唔合理？<br />\n咁我係新鴻基，我今次加價開源，下次減車節流。<br />\n到時你地係咪唔嘈？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115151_5037290bcede13dd7dcdfc5511330610.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115151_5037290bcede13dd7dcdfc5511330610.png&h=364db336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到尾，原來想一開始船都唔要。咁樣樓價仲平添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115156_70c8425af0e3f6555950a596f9dd482d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115156_70c8425af0e3f6555950a596f9dd482d.png&h=5a0ecc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115154_5037290bcede13dd7dcdfc5511330610.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115154_5037290bcede13dd7dcdfc5511330610.png&h=c8e66d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妖化完人，開始矮化人做小朋友同謾罵了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115157_860ca4dc97f350550514147215198d60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115157_860ca4dc97f350550514147215198d60.png&h=ea9d0ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新鴻基以心建家都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115157_aef97870cee2f864e99f703c89869a81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115157_aef97870cee2f864e99f703c89869a81.png&h=f5b15191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地係咪搞唔清楚馬灣發展所謂環保城本身就已經好唔合邏輯 同香港發展好大矛盾？<br />\n點解一開始會信政府搞得好依個荒島<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/115158_cfbd4b6470c9f3d2ef9d6e1063f51a49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F115158_cfbd4b6470c9f3d2ef9d6e1063f51a49.png&h=03fbc9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加油，全香港得你地珀麗居民發聲<br />\n你地唔出聲，連民主大報毒果都唔理你地<br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/738189/page/9\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/738189/page/9</a> #211"},{"pid":"a34f7ab3daccf4aae3e2813773091853c10c444b","tid":740323,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T23:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122749_5308bec11470e513fd90a0cade51b829.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122749_5308bec11470e513fd90a0cade51b829.png&h=35bc5834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新鴻基都做唔住<br />\n無錢賺，唔係認為有其他人想做下話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122750_ac1b4185b9472f74cf7e1e40d6557dc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122750_ac1b4185b9472f74cf7e1e40d6557dc9.png&h=fb9e20f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n30%不明開支 係咪要搵老廉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122750_960f0e05f13fb76682e15305c955c2d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122750_960f0e05f13fb76682e15305c955c2d6.png&h=ce97b577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始教新鴻基做生意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122751_960f0e05f13fb76682e15305c955c2d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122751_960f0e05f13fb76682e15305c955c2d6.png&h=268025d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴皮發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122752_a20b40d02713fa5528c33db14eb38239.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122752_a20b40d02713fa5528c33db14eb38239.png&h=d64bb398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔舒服都唔得<br />\n係咪炒車佢負責？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122754_2c05304ab17e58c025324f28daf2f097.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122754_2c05304ab17e58c025324f28daf2f097.png&h=91fa36cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你地果度荒島一個 同人地新市鎮比公路，機鐵去埋你度好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122755_1840a4df80aa92f59400748fc27fdc46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122755_1840a4df80aa92f59400748fc27fdc46.png&h=f103e833&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122759_e3b822aeaebb1225628cf36b03a9b302.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122759_e3b822aeaebb1225628cf36b03a9b302.png&h=8dfac852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他還是個孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122759_d8e0daa52ce741e6b17e1b3cd772be06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122759_d8e0daa52ce741e6b17e1b3cd772be06.png&h=e95f350c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/122800_6921f68e6ae4a5d6044490cdc77c99e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F122800_6921f68e6ae4a5d6044490cdc77c99e4.png&h=b5a8f2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後段都唔係駁人<br />\n不斷話人細路<br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/738189/page/9\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/738189/page/9</a> #219"},{"pid":"31d3254f48a125fd39f8